@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gwyhck(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp - v0)
    tmp = wp.abs(0.22)
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.03)) + v2)
    tmp = ((0.24 + v1) * wp.abs((v2 + 0.31 / tmp + 0.52)))
    data[tid] = v0
